# Go generated protobuf bindings ARE committed (so `go install` works on a
# clean checkout / module-proxy fetch, which never runs `make proto`).
# The Dart bindings below stay generated-only; they're built by `flutter build`.

# Scratch — throwaway `fugo init` demo projects, plus manual-test screenshots
# and captured logs. Keep local experiments under .scratch/ so the repo root
# stays clean; nothing in here is part of the framework.
.scratch/
testapp/
myapp/
testproj/
counterapp/
m3test/
leetcode/

# Manual-test artifacts: root-level screenshots and captured stdout/stderr.
/*.png
*.out
*.err
